[H2] Background | When the Planner enters Step 2 (Choose Form) of the Create Daily Planning modal stepper, the system must return a list of available forms from  | maintenance-strategy |  relevant to the selected equipment. Asset Type has been removed from the UI design and is no longer required in the response. | [H2] Objective | Provide a new API endpoint that returns a list of forms filtered by equipment model and service type, for use in the Choose Form step during plan creation. | [H2] Scope | - Service:  | maintenance-strategy | - New endpoint: GET form list | [H2] Requirements | Request parameters: | No || Parameter || Type || Required || Description | 1 || equipmentModel || String || Yes || Equipment model derived from selected equipment in Step 1 | 2 || serviceType || String || No || Service type derived from Activity Type / Template selection in Step 1 | 3 || siteId || Integer || Yes || Site scoping from JWT | Response fields: | No || Field || Type || Description | 1 || formId || Guid || Unique identifier of the form | 2 || formName || String || Display name of the form | 3 || assetModel || String || Asset model tagged to the form | 4 || serviceType || String || Service type tagged to the form | 5 || maintenanceCategoryType || String || Maintenance category type tagged to the form | 6 || version || Integer || Current active version of the form | 7 || matchType || String || "model+service" |  or  | "model_only" |  — indicates which filter the form matched | Note:  | assetType |  has been  | removed |  from the response — it is no longer displayed in the UI. | [H2] Business Rules | - Forms matching both  | equipmentModel |  AND  | serviceType |  are returned first ( | matchType = "model+service" | ). | - Forms matching  | equipmentModel |  only are returned second ( | matchType = "model_only" | ). | - Only active, published forms are returned ( | IsActive = 1 | ,  | Status = Published | ). | - TenantCode scoped from JWT — cross-tenant data must not be returned. | - If no forms match, return empty array (not an error). | [H2] Acceptance Criteria | - Endpoint returns form list grouped by  | matchType | :  | model+service |  results appear before  | model_only |  results. | - Only active published forms are included in the response. | - Empty array returned when no matching forms exist — not a 4xx error. | - TenantCode isolation enforced — forms from other tenants not returned. | - Response includes all required fields per table above. | - assetType |  is NOT included in the response. | - Endpoint returns within acceptable latency under normal load. | [H2] Form Suggestion Grouping (wajib diimplementasi) | Response harus mengembalikan form dalam DUA grup terurut — Grup 1 lebih relevan, ditampilkan lebih atas di FE: | Grup || Filter || Deskripsi | Grup 1 || Equipment Model + Service Type match || Form yang di-mapping ke kombinasi model DAN service type yang bersangkutan. Paling relevan. | Grup 2 || Equipment Model only || Form yang di-mapping ke model saja, tanpa filter service type. | Planner juga bisa melakukan pencarian manual untuk menemukan form di luar kedua grup tersebut. | [H2] Default IsMandatory untuk Service Sheet | Jika response mengandung form bertipe Service Sheet (mapping ke Equipment Model + Service Hour yang sesuai), server harus menyertakan flag isSuggestedMandatory=true sebagai hint ke FE. FE menampilkan toggle IsMandatory dalam posisi ON sebagai default suggestion. | Authority IsMandatory sepenuhnya ada di Planner — flag ini hanya suggestion awal. Planner bebas mengubah nilai IsMandatory untuk semua form termasuk service sheet. | [H3] Contoh response structure | [
  {
    "group": 1,
    "formCode": "SS-HD785-250",
    "formName": "Service Sheet HD785 250H",
    "isSuggestedMandatory": true   // hint: service sheet, default mandatory
  },
  {
    "group": 1,
    "formCode": "TYRE-HD785",
    "formName": "Tyre R&I Form HD785",
    "isSuggestedMandatory": false
  },
  {
    "group": 2,
    "formCode": "WELDING-GEN",
    "formName": "Welding Form",
    "isSuggestedMandatory": false
  }
] | [H3] Acceptance Criteria (tambahan) | - Response mengembalikan field "group" dengan nilai 1 atau 2 per form. | - Grup 1 selalu mendahului Grup 2 dalam response array. | - Service sheet yang matching Equipment Model + Service Type diberi isSuggestedMandatory=true. | - Form di luar kedua grup tidak dikembalikan (Planner cari via manual search). | - Test: serviceType provided -> Grup 1 dan 2 populated; serviceType null -> semua masuk Grup 2; model tidak match -> empty result.
